title: Saint Joseph's Claims Southern Maine Fall Classic Title (Saint Joseph's College of Maine Athletics)
text: ( Source : Saint Joseph's College of Maine Athletics ) GORHAM, Maine - The Saint Joseph 's College golf team led after 18 holes and maintained the advantage through the final 18 to win the USM Fall Classic , which was hosted at Gorham Country
